      "description": "The John Hancock Hedged Equity ETF (JHDG) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in large cap equity. The fund is actively managed, providing exposure to US large-cap stocks along with a flexible options overlay strategy. The fund seeks long-term capital appreciation while hedging market downturns. JHDG was launched on Apr 8, 2026 and is issued by John Hancock.",
